    public interface IndexingTransducer
extends com.google.common.base.Function<com.hp.hpl.jena.rdf.model.Resource,NamedFields>
    An IndexingTransducer is moved in a path across an LDPath backend and executes a single indexing tranformation, producing a NamedFields as the result of each execution. The path of the head is normally a collection or stream of Resources.
